author: The Current
description:
Eric Burton of Black Pumas gives thanks to The Current for their support early on in the band’s career.

The Current’s 20th anniversary is here — join us all year long as we celebrate the music that brought us together and keeps us together.

Find more at https://www.thecurrent.org/anniversary

Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube

description:
